high_descs: Turn left then face the counter to your right.
Take the lettuce off of the counter in front of you.
Turn right then face the sink on your left.
Wash the lettuce in the sink in front of you and take it out.
Turn around and face the fridge in front of you.
Place the lettuce inside of the fridge in front of you and close it.
anns.task_desc: Place clean lettuce in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn left, hang a right at the stove and walk to the counter ahead.
Pick up the head of lettuce from the left side of the counter.
Turn right and walk to the sink on the left.
Put the head of lettuce inside the sink, rinse it for a few seconds and pick it back up.
Turn around and walk to the black fridge ahead.
Put the rinsed head of lettuce inside the fridge on the bottom shelf to the left side and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed head of lettuce in a fridge.

high_descs: Walk a step forward then turn left and walk all the way to the counter in front of you then turn right and walk to the counter.
Pick up the head of lettuce that's in front of you.
Take two steps to your right so you face the right side of the sink.
Wash the lettuce in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Put the lettuce in the fridge then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean head of lettuce in the fridge.
